:H2.Obtaining the Current Layout
:P.
The current layout definitions may be obtained
by converting the definitions into a text file.
:XMP.
&gml.LAYOUT.
&gml.CONVERT file='currlay'.
&gml.eLAYOUT.
:eXMP.
:PC.
The file CURRLAY.GML will be created by processing the above
text with &WGML..
Since no other layout sections are specified, the produced information
will be the default layout which is built into &WGML..
